data.description: Main level master allows for single level living with the additional benefit of three spacious bedrooms and a loft upstairs.  Backing to a green belt this beautiful home is ready for you to enjoy.  The main floor features expansive vaulted ceilings in the living room, a spacious master bedroom with a five-piece master bath, and a eat in kitchen with incredible storage.  The dining room has been converted to a music room but has ample space for your dining room furniture.  Upstairs the three bedrooms all are nice sized, with great storage in the closets, and have the added benefit of easy access to a loft (perfect for a game room!).  The entire interior has been freshly painted and has new carpet.  The unfinished basement is great for storage or could be easily finished for additional living area.   The south facing driveway means snow melts!
